name: Blue and white floral dress for Barbie Doll - ed27
description:
This is a cute little summer dress for Barbie.

It is made out of a cotton blend material with a blue floral print on a white background.

It has white ribbon straps and delicate white and gold lace at the hemline.

It has velcro to close the back.

The dress comes with a pair of royal blue heels.

The listing is for the dress only and does not include the shoes.

This comes from a smoke free home.

name: Pink & green floral semi-formal dress for Barbie Dolls - ed114
description:
This is a beautiful handmade semi-formal dress for your Barbie Doll.

It is made out of a cotton blend fabric for easy care.

The dress is an all over pattern with green, pink, mauve and maroon flowers.

It has a full gathered skirt and a fitted bodice.

The shoulder straps and the belt are made out of the sale fabric as the dress.

Snaps are used to close the back of the dress and the belt.

A pair of shoes are included to complete the look.

The listing is for the clothes only and does not include the doll or the doll stand.

This comes from a smoke free home.
